<style>
	.left,
	.right {
		display: inline-block;
		width: 180px;
		vertical-align: top;
	}
</style>


<div id="identity_requester" class="form-placeholder">
	
		<p>
			To subscribe to our services, please click the "Request My Identity" button.
			      The unique identity credentials you receive are
			<strong>confidentialâ€”keep them safe and do not share them with anyone.</strong>
		</p>
		<p>
